</h5>
<div class="problem"><p>Verify that the set $R^\prime=\set{\vect{v}_1,\,\vect{v}_2,\,\vect{v}_4}$ at the end of <a class="knowl" acro="RSC5" type="Example" title="Reducing a span in $\complex{5}$" knowl="./knowls/example.RSC5.knowl">Example RSC5</a> is linearly independent.
</p></div>
</div><div class="exercise" acro="LDS.C50">
