</h5>
<div class="problem"><p>At the conclusion of <a class="knowl" acro="RSC4" type="Example" title="Reducing a span in $\complex{4}$" knowl="./knowls/example.RSC4.knowl">Example RSC4</a> two alternative solutions, sets $T^{\prime}$ and $T^{*}$, are proposed.  Verify these claims by proving that $\spn{T}=\spn{T^{\prime}}$ and $\spn{T}=\spn{T^{*}}$.
</p></div>
</div><div class="exercise" acro="LDS.T40">
<h5 class="exercise">
